Title: Determinant Representations for Correlation Functions of Spin-1/2 XXX
  and XXZ Heisenberg Magnets
Authors: F.H.L. Essler, H. Frahm, A.G. Izergin, V.E. Korepin
Comments: 23 pages, TeX, BONN-TH-94-14, revised version: typos corrected
Journal-ref: Commun.Math.Phys. 174 (1995) 191-214
\\
  We consider correlation functions of the spin-$\half$ XXX and XXZ Heisenberg
chains in a magnetic field. Starting from the algebraic Bethe Ansatz we derive
representations for various correlation functions in terms of determinants of
Fredholm integral operators.
